text: Bad Oeynhausen is a spa town in Minden-Lübbecke in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. About 49,000 people live there. It is on the left bank of the Weser river. == Twin towns == Bad Oeynhausen is twinned with: * Fismes, France * Inowrocław, Poland == References == == Other websites == * Category:Spa towns in Germany Category:Minden-Lübbecke Rural District
title: Bad Oeynhausen
